## Executive Summary
Your project shows solid fundamentals and demonstrates good understanding of game programming concepts. You've implemented a day/night transformation platformer with collision detection, level loading, and spatial hashing. However, there are several critical issues that need addressing before submission, particularly around memory management and code organization.

**Lines of Code**: ~1,264 (excluding tinyxml2 library)
**Theme Implementation**: ✅ Day/Night transformation mechanic

